================================================================================
                      RECOMMENDATIONS & CONCLUSIONS
================================================================================

Power Profile: EXCELLENT
  - Total power (18.2 mW) is very low
  - Suitable for battery-powered applications
  - Device operating at optimal efficiency point

Design Status:
  ✓ Well below power budget
  ✓ Excellent thermal characteristics
  ✓ No thermal management required
  ✓ No power optimization needed

Recommendations:
  1. Keep design as-is - power consumption is acceptable
  2. Ensure proper PCB layout with adequate bypass capacitors
  3. Use 1.0V and 3.3V regulators with >85% efficiency
  4. Implement decoupling as specified in thermal section
  5. No active cooling required

Operating Conditions:
  - Safe for continuous operation at 25-85°C
  - Maximum power margin available
  - No throttling or power management needed

